wordGroup: symmetrical distribution 对称分布，对称分配

sentences.en: The two wings of the building are exactly symmetrical.
sentences.cn: 这座大厦的两翼完全对称。

sentences.en: She likes to talk about symmetrical and asymmetrical triangles.
sentences.cn: 她喜欢谈论对称和不对称的三角形。

sentences.en: It often times repeats and it can be symmetrical in that sense.
sentences.cn: 它经常重复并且感觉是对称的。
